# BON2020_LIS spectra tabulated for shieldSim
# Source model: Badhwar-O'Neill 2020 LIS parameters (Z=1 and Z=2)
# Energy column: total kinetic energy [MeV]
# Flux columns: differential flux [particles / (m^2 sr s MeV)]
# NOTE:
#   proton flux is tabulated directly versus total kinetic energy (same as MeV/n for A=1)
#   alpha flux is converted from BON2020's MeV/n representation to total kinetic energy:
#       E_total = 4*T_n,  flux_per_MeV(total) = flux_per_MeV_per_nucleon / 4
# Columns:
#   E_MeV_total   proton_flux   alpha_flux
